These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
Hobby: traveling, chess, puzzles, writing
Pet: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. Pet:rat is not to the right of Pet:ferret##8
2. Pet:rat is on the right of Hobby:traveling##1
3. Hobby:chess is on the left or right of Hobby:puzzles##3
4. Hobby:writing is somewhere to the right of Pet:guinea-pig##5
5. Hobby:writing is not to the left of Pet:rat##8
6. Pet:hamster is somewhere to the left of Hobby:chess##5
7. Hobby:chess is somewhere between Hobby:traveling and Pet:guinea-pig##7
8. Hobby:chess and Pet:rat have the same parity positions##9
9. Hobby:puzzles and Pet:ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | traveling | chess | puzzles     | writing |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

