5. Sport:snowboarding is somewhere to the left of Beverage:almond-milk##5
6. Beverage:almond-milk is somewhere to the right of Sport:lacrosse##5
7. Beverage:coffee is somewhere to the right of Beverage:almond-milk##5
8. Beverage:tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | snowboarding | lacrosse | handball      | biathlon |

